summary: Jeneva can be found working at the Solitude sawmill. She has experience with both axe and bow. CNHF v2_5 Standalone Body.
descriptionHtml:
Jeneva Minor or Jeneva the younger is an Imperial woman born and raised in Skyrim. She spends her days chopping down trees and hunting small game. She can be found working at the Solitude sawmill. Harvesting lumber has given her plenty of experience with an axe and she's learned quite a bit from bow hunting.


Fun Facts;
Level 6-80
Protected
Lumberjack
Potential Marriage Faction
No Crime
